<br>
We do not allow half elves, High Elves, Wood Elves  you get the idea.  <br>
<br>
Even though we would dearly love the benefits of a tracker, we don't accept bards either.  Bards used to be able to choose Evil but now we go with selections at Birth.  Monks are taken on a case by case as some are good and some are not so good.<br>
<br>
